<name>BRAKE</name>
<section id="1000N_S000N" variety="S000N">
<name>BRAKE</name>
<ttl id="1000N_S000N_7A80K_T004Y" variety="T004Y">
<name>FRONT BRAKE</name>
<para id="RM0000010KR00WX" category="G" type-id="3001K" name-id="BR0UA-01" from="201202">
<name>INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM0000010KR00WX_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM0000010KR00WX_01_0001" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00001PQ00000">
<ptxt>CHECK BRAKE CYLINDER AND PISTON</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Check the cylinder bore and piston for rust or scoring.</ptxt>
<ptxt>If necessary, replace the cylinder and piston.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000010KR00WX_01_0002" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00001PR00000">
<ptxt>CHECK PAD LINING THICKNESS</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C133733" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a ruler, measure the pad lining thickness.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Standard thickness</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>10.0 mm (0.394 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<spec>
<title>Minimum thickness</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>1.0 mm (0.039 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the pad lining thickness is equal to or less than the minimum, replace the pad.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000010KR00WX_01_0003" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00001PS00000">
<ptxt>CHECK FRONT DISC BRAKE PAD SUPPORT PLATE</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Check the 4 plates.</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>Make sure that the plates have sufficient rebound and are free from deformation, cracks wear, rust and dirt.</ptxt>
</atten4>
<ptxt>If necessary, replace the plates.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000010KR00WX_01_0004" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00001PT00000">
<ptxt>CHECK DISC THICKNESS</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C111368" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a micrometer, measure the disc thickness.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Standard thickness</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>28.0 mm (1.102 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<spec>
<title>Minimum thickness</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>26.0 mm (1.024 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the disc thickness is less than the minimum, replace the disc.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
